Title: Three of a Kind
Plot: While on a stakeout of a Government Defense Convention in Las Vegas, The Lone Gunmen are reunited with Susanne Modeski, the mysterious woman who disappeared ten years earlier when they first met Agent Mulder.
GuestStars: Signy Coleman, Charles Rocket, John Billingsley, Jim Fyfe, Michael McKean, George Sharperson, Brian Reddy, Phil Abrams, Richard Zobel, Jeff Bowser, Jason Felipe, Rick Garcia, Kalena Coleman
